quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  45,1,"Ha-meem"
  45,2,"Tanzeelu alkitabi mina AllahialAAazeezi alhakeem"
  45,3,"Inna fee assamawati wal-ardilaayatin lilmu/mineen"
  45,4,"Wafee khalqikum wama yabuththu min dabbatinayatun liqawmin yooqinoon"
  45,5,"Wakhtilafi allayli wannahariwama anzala Allahu mina assama-i minrizqin faahya bihi al-arda baAAda mawtihawatasreefi arriyahi ayatunliqawmin yaAAqiloon"
  45,6,"Tilka ayatu Allahinatlooha AAalayka bilhaqqi fabi-ayyi hadeethinbaAAda Allahi waayatihi yu/minoon"
  45,7,"Waylun likulli affakin atheem"
  45,8,"YasmaAAu ayati Allahitutla AAalayhi thumma yusirru mustakbiran kaan lamyasmaAAha fabashshirhu biAAathabin aleem"
  45,9,"Wa-itha AAalima min ayatinashay-an ittakhathaha huzuwan ola-ika lahumAAathabun muheen"
  45,10,"Min wara-ihim jahannamu walayughnee AAanhum ma kasaboo shay-an wala maittakhathoo min dooni Allahi awliyaa walahumAAathabun AAatheem"